Human rights activist Aisha Yesufu has weigh-in, on the controversy surrounding the presidential candidate of the people’s Democratic Party PDP, Atiku Abubakar presidential ambition.


According to the Nigerian activist and businesswoman, Aisha Yesufu, Wike is working financially to ensure the party’s unity while Atiku Abubaker, is in Dubai having fun and chilling with the big boys. Speaking further, she said while Atiku Abubaker is busy having fun in Dubai, he left his fans who are busy attacking people who are not in support of his presidency on social media.
Aisha Yesufu’s statement was not unconnected with Atiku’s neglect of the PDP candidate, Bisi Kolawole Who Lost in the just concluded gubernatorial election in Ekiti. The party stalwarts said Atiku’s Failure to canvass for Bisi Kolawole, contributed to the party’s loss in the ekiti gubernatorial election.
A few minutes after voicing her opinion about Atiku Abubaker Presidential ambition, some of her Fans went to the comments to express their views. Here is a screenshot
